<br>
Thule is your lord and creator, Iksar, you cannot change or deny what you are.  <br>
How DARE you turn your back on those who gave you life! Pretending to bow <br>
to false gods is heresy and punishable by slow death. <br>
<br>
Our lord Thule chooses to take mortal form, an Avatar to show his great might <br>
to all. Twice I have seen his power as he crushed dozens of soft skins who <br>
dared to rise against him.  I saw the mounts of broken bodies piled about me, <br>
and kneeled humbly before such greatness.<br>
<br>
Yes you deserve to die, crusader.  You are hereby banned for the rest of your <br>
miserable existence. New Sebilis, proud city of your ancestors,  is forever <br>
closed to you and will lead to death by torture shoult you attempt to <br>
return, so say our ancient laws.<br>
<br>
You are NOT in a position to request. Indeed your exile is signed and has <br>
been proclaimed inside our mighty walls.  Pray  you hide well Forsaken, for <br>
I and the other Skathris, loyal servants of Emperor Vekin, will chase you to <br>
the ends of Norrath, and burn your status of outcast into your very scales, <br>
for all to witness, the rest of your sorry days.<br>
<br>
Your people forget you, Sariyathai, your existence faded from history's pages.<br>
<br>
Glory to the Empire!<br>
<br>
